message: Dear Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product, which holds immense value for us at $12000. Considering its exceptional quality and benefits, I believe it would be a great addition to your collection. I am offering this exclusive item to you at a special price of $11000. This is an opportunity not to be missed, as it offers significant savings while securing a high-quality asset. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
